Nobody Knows About the Persian Cats;;76;;95;;NC;;Two young musicians, Negar (Negar Shaghaghi) and Ashkan (Ashkan Koshanejad), are released from prison. They immediately immerse themselves in the underground rock scene in Tehran, Iran -- "underground" because playing in public venues is outlawed. They plan to escape from their repressive country to play a concert in Europe, but first they need to find a rhythm section and some passports. They place their hope in Nader (Hamed Behdad), a savvy fixer who promises to get them to their gig.;;Drama;;Bahman Ghobadi;;2009;;Negar Shaghaghi,Ashkan Koshanejad,Hamed Behdad;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/no_one_knows_about_persian_cats